# 💻 Practical Implementation

Example cloud services used in production systems.

| Layer         | AWS Service                       | Azure Equivalent    |
| ------------- | --------------------------------- | ------------------- |
| Compute       | EC2 (Elastic Compute Cloud)       | Virtual Machines    |
| Load Balancer | ALB (Application Load Balancer)   | Azure Load Balancer |
| Database      | RDS (Relational Database Service) | Azure SQL           |
| Storage       | S3 (Simple Storage Service)       | Azure Blob Storage  |
| Cache         | ElastiCache                       | Azure Redis         |

