# 🧠 Cloud Architect Mindset

Cloud architects always think about **failure scenarios**.

Key questions they ask:

• What happens if a server fails?
• What happens if traffic spikes suddenly?
• What happens if a region goes down?
• How can infrastructure cost be reduced?

Production architecture must always prioritize:

✔ Reliability
✔ Scalability
✔ Security
✔ Cost Efficiency

